reviewText: Ordered twice, both times the video was broken.
Used this as a training tool while teaching at the leadership academy in the military.  This is an awesome training tool for adults and children.
My husband absolutely loves this set. He saw it "shared" on facebook and then he started looking it up and couldn't believe the prices...but i surprised him and he loves it.
I wish everyone would watch this program. It's especially useful for school programs. It is very powerful and filled with truth!
